#: doc/en/get-started.md:50
msgid "## Create the spaces (tables)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:52
msgid ""
"The library is built on 12 tables. Create them in the following order to "
"make relations easier to define: first the reference tables, then the main "
"tables, then the join tables, and finally the transaction table."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:54
msgid "### 1 â Reference tables"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:56
msgid "These tables have no dependency on other tables."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#: doc/en/get-started.md:60
msgid "In the **Data** section of the sidebar, click **+**."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
#: doc/en/get-started.md:60
msgid "Enter the space name and confirm."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '3. '
#: doc/en/get-started.md:60
msgid "Repeat for each table."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:68
msgid ""
"| Space | Role | |--------|------| | `genres` | Literary genres (novel, "
"comic, non-fiction, â¦) | | `auteurs` | Book authors | | `classes` | School "
"classes | | `motscles` | Thematic keywords | | `etiquettes` | Classification "
"labels (prize, favorites, â¦) |"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:70
