#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:130
msgid "### Computed column (Î»)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:133
msgid ""
"Select **Computed column** and enter a MoonScript or Lua expression.  The "
"formula is the body of a function `(self, space) -> <expression>`; in "
"MoonScript `@field` accesses `self.field`. The value is recomputed on each "
"read and is not stored."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Example: `nom_complet` in `auteurs`** â combine first name, particle and last name while handling nulls:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:143 doc/en/reference.md:149
msgid ""
"```moonscript parts = {} table.insert(parts, @prenom) if @prenom and "
"@prenom != \"\" table.insert(parts, @particule) if @particule and "
"@particule != \"\" table.insert(parts, @nom) if @nom and @nom != \"\" table."
"concat(parts, \" \")  ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:145
msgid ""
"The `space` parameter gives access to records of another space (full scan):"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:153
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"```moonscript\n"
"-- Count available copies for this book\n"
"n = 0\n"
"for e in *space(\"exemplaires\")\n"
"  n += 1 if e.livre_id == @id and e.disponible\n"
"n\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:155
msgid "### Trigger formula ((trigger))"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:158
msgid ""
"Select **Trigger formula** and optionally list the trigger fields.  The "
"formula is executed and the result **stored** on each creation or "
"modification of the listed fields."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Example: `cote_auto` in `livres`** â generate an automatic shelf mark from the first three letters of the title and the year (triggered on `titre` and `annee`):\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/en/get-started.md:167 doc/en/reference.md:162
msgid ""
"```moonscript -- triggerFields: [\"titre\", \"annee\"] prefix = (@titre or "
"\"\")\\upper!\\sub(1, 3)\\gsub(\"[^%A]\", \"\")  annee = if @annee then "
"tostring(@annee) else \"????\" \"#{prefix}-#{annee}\" ```"
msgstr ""

